<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Panorama Hills</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-xl">The idyllic surroundings, the picturesque parks, and the multiple biking trails, render the community in Panorama Hills a perfect neighborhood for raising a family or spending a tranquil and convenient life post-retirement.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The community is also renowned for its state-of-the-art sports and recreation facility called the Cardel Place that offers excellent entertainment services for the local residents.</p>

